-- Swiss Man Sentenced to Three Strokes of Cane, Jail for Singapore Vandalism
-- Andrea Tan
-- 2010-06-25T10:35:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-25/swiss-man-sentenced-to-three-strokes-of-cane-jail-for-singapore-vandalism.html

          
          
             Oliver Fricker, an executive at
financial software maker Comit AG, was sentenced to three
strokes of the cane and five months in jail for breaking into a
Singapore depot and spray-painting a commuter train.  
